title: Catholic Lady Throat Chop!
description: Kyle and Ethan talk about some weird news reported by Not The Bee including a lady getting throat-chopped by another lady during a Catholic Church service and a weird looking sheep that sold for $500,000.

title: Bee Headlines Banned Before Publication
description: Kyle and Ethan share headlines that never made it onto the Babylon Bee because they were too spicy, too cold, or too stupid.

title: Large Turnout At Memorial For Hans Gruber Who Was Thrown From A Building By A Police Officer
description: “That man was a hero,” said Doyle Graham, who traveled from Nevada to pay respects. “I mean, I don’t really know much about him other than that some police officer killed him, but he seems like someone we should all honor and emulate.”
